snippet.textDisplay:
Thank you Cleetus, for reigniting the passion inside of me in this dark and boring part of my life. Your videos have definitively impacted some lives in ways you could never imagine.
I'm currently studying Civil Engineering and this video inspired me so much, as it was a confirmation that I'm studying to do something I love and actually gave me a lot of cool ideas as to what I could do in the future!
This is my 3rd week of quarantine, and my motivation to watch online classes was almost gone, due to the news that my country has extended its State of Emergency for 2 more weeks.
By the way, I would like to congratulate 3 16 guys, they did an absolute mint job! The quality and speed on their part were top-notch and yet being 10% under budget is mindblowing! Awesome job!
